release_notes:
This is a Windows only hotfix from the 2023.3.412.0 release
 
## Notable updates
- Fixed issue where certain split tunnel configurations with certain multicast IPs not excluded couldn't connect. 224.0.0.0/4 and ff00::/8 are now always excluded from the tunnel on Windows.
- Fixed a connectivity issue that was more likely to happen for clients with large host-based split tunnel rules

## Known issues
No known issues
 
For Zero Trust documentation please see: https://developers.cloudflare.com/cloudflare-one/connections/connect-devices/warp
For Consumer documentation please see: https://developers.cloudflare.com/warp-client/
